description: Plouf Plouf Gastronomie is a rustic French mobile bistro like you've never seen! From our professional, mobile kitchen, husband and wife team Anik and Mario Molliere (a French Master Chef) serve organic, all natural, seasonal dishes prepared a la minute. We source ingredients of the highest quality from New England farms with a commitment to organic, humane and sustainable practices. "LIKE US" to find where the Plouf Plouf Truck is each day or inquire about our catering, private parties and soirees! (but of course!)
name: Plouf Plouf Gastronomie
